    • AlgsExternalConnector

      public AlgsExternalConnector(String id, String algorithmName, String[] hyperParams, String prePostproc, String metricsNames)
      Constructor of the learning API connector
      Parameters:
      id - Identificator of the problem (must be unique)
      algorithmName - Algorithm to use
      hyperParams - List of the hyperparametres values for the algorithm, null if there is none
      prePostproc - Name of class that contains the pre and post processing methods to apply to the data, null if no processing method is needed
